recitals:
,
Having regard to the Treaty on European Union and in particular Article 18(5) thereof,
Having regard to Common Position 98/633/CFSP(1),
(1) Whereas Common Position 98/633/CFSP aims at consolidating support for the Royaumont Process on stability and good-neighbourliness in South-East Europe;
(2) Whereas the contribution of the Royaumont Process Coordinator; Mr Roumeliotis, has been instrumental in the development of the Process;
(3) Whereas with a view to the consolidation and continuation of the work carried out so far, the Coordinator should be provided with the logistical base and the human resources needed to continue to carry out his functions,
